Lekhwiya]]\n|{{flagicon|QAT}}\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"|July 2014\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"|July 2015\n{{WDL|41|28|8|5|for=82|against=43|diff=yes}}\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[Al-Rayyan SC|Al Rayyan]]\n|{{flagicon|QAT}}\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"|October 2016\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"|July 2018\n{{WDL|73|39|15|19|for=154|against=107|diff=yes}}\n|-\n|colspan=4|'''Total'''\n{{WDLtot|445|214|106|125|for=737|against=529|diff=yes}}\n|}\n\n==Honours==\n\n===Player===\n'''Juventus'''\n*[[Intercontinental Cup (football)|Intercontinental Cup]]: [[1985 Intercontinental Cup|1985]]\n*[[Serie A]]: [[1985\u201386 Serie A|1985\u201386]]\n\n'''Barcelona'''\n*[[Copa del Rey]]: [[1990 Copa del Rey Final|1989\u201390]]\n*[[La Liga]] (4): [[1990\u201391 La Liga|1990\u201391]], [[1991\u201392 La Liga|1991\u201392]], [[1992\u201393 La Liga|1992\u201393]], [[1993\u201394 La Liga|1993\u201394]]\n*[[Supercopa de Espa\u00f1a]] (2): [[1991 Supercopa de Espa\u00f1a|1991]], [[1992 Supercopa de Espa\u00f1a|1992]]\n*[[European Cup]]: [[1992 European Cup Final|1991\u201392]]\n*[[UEFA Super Cup]]: [[1992 European Super Cup|1992]]\n\n'''Real Madrid'''\n*[[La Liga]]: [[1994\u201395 La Liga|1994\u201395]]\n\n'''Ajax'''\n*[[Eredivisie]]: [[1997\u201398 Eredivisie|1997\u201398]]\n*[[KNVB Cup]]: [[1997\u201398 KNVB Cup|1997\u201398]]\n\n'''Denmark'''\n*[[FIFA Confederations Cup]]: [[1995 King Fahd Cup|1995]]\n\n'''Individual'''\n*[[Danish Football Player of the Year|Danish Player of the Year]] (2): 1982, 1985\n*[[Don Bal\u00f3n Award]]&nbsp;\u2013 [[La Liga]] Best Foreign Player of the Year: 1991\u201392\n*[[European Sports Media|ESM Team of the Year]]: 1994\u201395<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rsssf.com/miscellaneous/esm-xi.html |title=ESM XI |publisher=Rec.Sport.Soccer Statistics Foundation |accessdate=13 April 2015 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160207144925/http://www.rsssf.com/miscellaneous/esm-xi.html |archivedate= 7 February 2016 }}</ref>\n*[[FIFA|FIFA XI]] (Reserve): 1996<ref>[http://www.rsssf.com/miscellaneous/fifa-xi.html FIFA XI\u00b4s Matches&nbsp;\u2013 Full Info] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117033752/http://www.rsssf.com/miscellaneous/fifa-xi.html |date=17 November 2015 }}</ref>\n*[[FIFA World Cup awards#All-Star Team|FIFA World Cup All-Star Team]]: 1998<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.fifa.com/newscentre/news/newsid=71747/index.html|title=MasterCard All-Star Team of the 1998 World Cup|publisher=FIFA|date=10 July 1998|accessdate=24 November 2016}}</ref>\n*Best Foreign Player in [[Football in Spain|Spanish Football]] in the last 25 years: 1974\u20131999<ref name=\"BBC Sport2\">{{cite news|url = https://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/18325287 |title=Michael Laudrup named new Swansea City manager |publisher=BBC Sport|date=15 June 2012|accessdate=30 December 2015}}</ref>\n*[[UEFA Jubilee Awards|UEFA Golden Player]] (Greatest Danish Footballer of the last 50 Years): 2003<ref name=jubilee1/>\n*[[FIFA 100]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/international/2374252/Pele-open-to-ridicule-over-top-hundred.html|title=Pele open to ridicule over top hundred|work=The Telegraph|author1=Christopher Davies|date=5 March 2004|accessdate=9 July 2015}}</ref>\n*[[Denmark national football team#Best players of all time|Denmark's Best Player of All Time]]: 2006<ref name=\"BBC Sport2\"/>\n*Scandinavia Best Player Ever: 2015<ref name=\"BT Sport\">{{cite web|url=http://www.bt.dk/fodbold/laudrup-kaaret-til-nordens-bedste|title=Laudrup k\u00e5ret til Nordens bedste|publisher=BT Sport|accessdate=29 December 2015}}</ref>\n*[[Denmark national football team#Hall of Fame|Danish Football Hall of Fame]]\n*[[World Soccer Magazine|World Soccer The Greatest Players of the 20th century]]: The 100 Greatest Footballers of All Time<ref>[http://www.rsssf.com/miscellaneous/best-x-players-of-y.html#ws100 World Soccer: The 100 Greatest Footballers of All Time] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151231035356/http://www.rsssf.com/miscellaneous/best-x-players-of-y.html |date=31 December 2015 }} Retrieved 30 December 2015</ref>\n\n===Manager===\n'''Br\u00f8ndby'''\n*[[Danish Superliga]]: [[2004\u201305 Danish Superliga|2004\u201305]]\n*[[Danish Cup]]: [[2002\u201303 Danish Cup|2002\u201303]], [[2004\u201305 Danish Cup|2004\u201305]]\n*[[Danish Supercup]]: 2002\n\n'''Swansea City'''\n*[[Football League Cup]]: [[2012\u201313 Football League Cup|2012\u201313]]\n\n'''Lekhwiya'''\n*[[Qatar Stars League]]: [[2014\u201315 Qatar Stars League|2014\u201315]]\n*[[Qatar Crown Prince Cup|Crown Prince Cup]]: [[Qatar Crown Prince Cup|2014\u201315]]\n\n'''Individual'''\n*Danish Manager of the Year: 2002\u201303, 2004\u201305\n*[[Qatar Stars League]] Manager of the Month: [[2014\u201315 Qatar Stars League#Awards|August 2014]], [[2014\u201315 Qatar Stars League#Awards|December 2014]]\n\n===Orders===\n*[[Order of the Dannebrog]]: 2000\n\n==Films==\n* {{in lang|da}} [[J\u00f8rgen Leth]], \"''Michael Laudrup&nbsp;\u2013 en fodboldspiller''\", Denmark, 1993\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}} <!--- 111.https://www.juvenews.eu/notizie-juve/cabrini-laudrup-il-piu-forte-con-cui-ho-giocato-lo-diceva-anche-platini/ --->\n\n==Sources==\n* {{cite book|ref=Kvist|author=Jakob Kvist|title=Ambassad\u00f8ren&nbsp;\u2013 en bog om Michael Laudrup|place=Denmark|year= 1996 |isbn= 87-583-1285-4|language=Danish}}\n\n==Further reading==\n* {{in lang|it}} Bruno Bernardi, \"Michael Laudrup\", Italy, 1986\n* {{in lang|da}} Flemming Nielsen and Vagn Nielsen, \"''Fodboldkunstneren Michael Laudrup : rundt om en stjerne''\", Denmark, 1986\n* {{in lang|da}} Michael Laudrup, \"''Mod nye m\u00e5l''\", Denmark, 1989, {{ISBN|87-559-0848-9}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category}}\n*{{NFT player}}\n* {{BDFutbol|1966}}\n* {{BDFutbol manager|1966}}\n* {{Cite web |url=http://www.realmadrid.com/cs/Satellite/en/1193041516860/1202817506365/jugador/JugadorLegendario/Laudrup.htm |title=Michael Laudrup at Real Madrid |access-date=1 September 2012 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130622123429/http://www.realmadrid.com/cs/Satellite/en/1193041516860/1202817506365/jugador/JugadorLegendario/Laudrup.htm |archive-date=22 June 2013 |url-status=dead |df=dmy-all }}\n* {{Cite web |url=http://www.brondby.com/player.asp?sid=30&id=33 |title=Br\u00f8ndby IF profile |access-date=8 January 2006 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20041010023914/http://www.brondby.com/player.asp?sid=30&id=33 |archive-date=10 October 2004 |url-status=dead |df=dmy-all |language=da}}\n* [http://www.dbu.dk/landshold/landsholdsdatabasen/PlayerInfo/1238 Danish national team profile] {{in lang|da}}\n* {{FIFA player|44298}}\n* {{WorldFootball.net|michael-laudrup}}\n*{{J.League player}}\n\n{{S-start}}\n{{s-sports}}\n{{succession box|title=[[Denmark national football team|Denmark]] captain|before=[[Lars Olsen]]|after=[[Peter Schmeichel]]|years=1994\u20131998}}\n{{S-end}}\n{{Navboxes colour\n|title = Denmark squads\n|bg = #e11b22\n|fg = white\n|bordercolor = silver\n|list1=\n{{Denmark squad UEFA Euro 1984}}\n{{Denmark squad 1986 FIFA World Cup}}\n{{Denmark squad UEFA Euro 1988}}\n{{Denmark squad 1995 King Fahd Cup}}\n{{Denmark squad UEFA Euro 1996}}\n{{Denmark squad 1998 FIFA World Cup}}\n}}\n{{Navboxes colour\n|title = Awards\n|bg = Gold\n|fg = Black\n|list1=\n{{1998 FIFA World Cup Team of the Tournament}}\n{{Danish Football Hall of Fame}}\n{{Danish Football Player of the Year}}\n{{Danish Football Manager of the Year}}\n{{La Liga Foreign Player of the Year}}\n{{FIFA 100}}\n{{UEFA Jubilee Awards}}\n{{Br\u00f8ndby IF Player of the Year}}\n}}\n{{Navboxes\n|title= Michael Laudrup managerial positions\n|list1=\n{{Br\u00f8ndby IF managers}}\n{{Getafe CF managers}}\n{{Spartak Moscow managers}}\n{{RCD Mallorca managers}}\n{{Swansea City A.F.C. managers}}\n}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Laudrup, Michael}}\n[[Category:1964 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Frederiksberg]]\