30\n|align=\"center\" |4\u20130\n|[[UEFA Euro 1996 qualifying Group 2|UEFA Euro 1996 qualifying]]\n|-\n|32\n|16 August 1995\n|[[Hrazdan Stadium]], Yerevan, Armenia\n|{{fb|Armenia}}\n|align=\"center\" |1\u20130\n|align=\"center\" |2\u20130\n|UEFA Euro 1996 qualifying\n|-\n|33\n|6 September 1995\n|[[King Baudouin Stadium]], Brussels, Belgium\n|{{fb|Belgium}}\n|align=\"center\" |1\u20130\n|align=\"center\" |3\u20131\n|UEFA Euro 1996 qualifying\n|-\n|34\n|15 November 1995\n|Parken Stadium, Copenhagen, Denmark\n|{{fb|Armenia}}\n|align=\"center\" |3\u20131\n|align=\"center\" |3\u20131\n|UEFA Euro 1996 qualifying\n|-\n|35\n|24 April 1996\n|Parken Stadium, Copenhagen, Denmark\n|{{fb|Scotland}}\n|align=\"center\" |1\u20130\n|align=\"center\" |2\u20130\n|Friendly\n|-\n|36\n|10 September 1997\n|Parken Stadium, Copenhagen, Denmark\n|{{fb|Croatia}}\n|align=\"center\" |2\u20130\n|align=\"center\" |3\u20131\n|[[1998 FIFA World Cup qualification \u2013 UEFA Group 1|1998 FIFA World Cup qualification]]\n|-\n|37\n|24 June 1998\n|[[Stade de Gerland]], Lyon, France\n|{{fb|France}}\n|align=\"center\" |1\u20131\n|align=\"center\" |1\u20132\n|[[1998 FIFA World Cup]]\n|}\n\n===Managerial statistics===\n{{updated|25 July 2018}}\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center\"\n|-\n! rowspan=2 style=\"width:120px;\"|Team\n! rowspan=2 style=\"width:10px;\"|Nat\n! rowspan=2 style=\"width:130px;\"|From\n! rowspan=2 style=\"width:130px;\"|To\n! colspan=8 |Record\n|-\n!G||W||D||L||GF||GA||GD||Win %\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[Br\u00f8ndby IF|Br\u00f8ndby]]\n|{{flagicon|DEN}}\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"|July 2002\n|align=\"left\"|June 2006\n{{WDL|132|76|31|25|for=237|against=119|diff=yes}}\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[Getafe CF|Getafe]]\n|{{flagicon|ESP}}\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"|July 2007\n|align=\"left\"|June 2008\n{{WDL|59|25|15|19|for=81|against=70|diff=yes}}\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[FC Spartak Moscow|Spartak Moscow]]\n|{{flagicon|RUS}}\n| style=\"text-align